       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.

      *    PRCSS-DSTIC
      *     01:승인대상조회 / 02:승인의견조회 / 03:결의록탭조회
           EVALUATE  XDJL0419-I-PRCSS-DSTIC
           WHEN  CO-CHA-01

      *        협의체구분 : 담당심사역 OR 협의위원
               IF  XDJL0419-I-CNGP-DSTIC         = CO-CHA-1

                   PERFORM S3100-QJL2761-CALL-RTN
                      THRU S3100-QJL2761-CALL-EXT
               ELSE

                   PERFORM S3200-QJL2762-CALL-RTN
                      THRU S3200-QJL2762-CALL-EXT
               END-IF

      *        승인대상조회건수가 존재할 경우
               IF  XDJL0419-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1    > ZERO

                   PERFORM VARYING WK-K FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   WK-K > XDJL0419-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

                      INITIALIZE       WK-TEMP-CUST-IDNFR

                      MOVE XDJL0419-O-CUST-IDNFR(WK-K)
                        TO WK-TEMP-CUST-IDNFR

      *               QJL1241
                      PERFORM S3300-QJL1241-CALL-RTN
                         THRU S3300-QJL1241-CALL-EXT

                   END-PERFORM
               END-IF

           WHEN  CO-CHA-02
           WHEN  CO-CHA-03
      *@       결의록 조회 (THKJL0005)
               PERFORM S3400-QJL2754-CALL-RTN
                  THRU S3400-QJL2754-CALL-EXT

230330*        첨부파일 조회(THKJL0002)
               PERFORM S3500-QJL4022-CALL-RTN
                  THRU S3500-QJL4022-CALL-EXT
           END-EVALUATE

           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ QJL1241 조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-QJL1241-CALL-RTN.

      *@   초기화
           INITIALIZE                  XQJL1241-IN

      *@   변수 MOVE

      *@  그룹회사구분코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL1241-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    전영업일 1개월전 날짜 구함
           PERFORM S5000-CJIIL03-CALL-RTN
              THRU S5000-CJIIL03-CALL-EXT

      *    전영업일 추출
           PERFORM S4000-CJIDT16-CALL-RTN
              THRU S4000-CJIDT16-CALL-EXT

      *@   기준년월일 - 전영업일 조회
      *   신청년월일의 전영업일로 조회해야함.
      *    MOVE JICOM-BF-BZOPR-YMD
           MOVE XCJIDT16-O-BF-BZOPR-YMD
             TO XQJL1241-I-BASE-YMD

      *@   월말구분(1:일,2:월)
           IF WK-BASEYMD < XQJL1241-I-BASE-YMD
               MOVE '1'
                 TO XQJL1241-I-ENMN-DSTIC
           ELSE
               MOVE '2'
                 TO XQJL1241-I-ENMN-DSTIC
           END-IF


      *@   KB-PIN (QJL2761 & QJL2762 OUT CUST-IDNFR)
           MOVE WK-TEMP-CUST-IDNFR
             TO XQJL1241-I-KB-PIN

      *@   고객관리부점코드
           MOVE SPACES
             TO XQJL1241-I-BRNCD1
           MOVE CO-CHA-9999
             TO XQJL1241-I-BRNCD2

220324*    조회구분(1:전체,2:설정,3:미설정)
           MOVE '1'
             TO XQJL1241-I-INQURY-DSTIC

      *@   SQLIO SELECT
           #DYSQLA QJL1241 SELECT XQJL1241-CA

      *@   결과확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
      *@            출력파라미터 조립
                    PERFORM S3310-QJL1241-OUTPUT-RTN
                       THRU S3310-QJL1241-OUTPUT-EXT
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장오픈에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 OPEN 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

           .
       S3300-QJL1241-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ QJL1241 OUTPUT SET
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-QJL1241-OUTPUT-RTN.

      *@   OUTPUT DATA PUT LOOP
           PERFORM VARYING WK-L FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   WK-L > DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
      *@       차주명
               MOVE XQJL1241-O-BRWR-NAME(WK-L)
                 TO XDJL0419-O-BRWR-NAME(WK-K)

      *@       신용등급（신청시）
               MOVE XQJL1241-O-CRDRAT1(WK-L)
                 TO XDJL0419-O-APLCN-CRDRAT(WK-K)

      *@       신용등급（최근）
               MOVE XQJL1241-O-CRDRAT2(WK-L)
                 TO XDJL0419-O-CRDRAT(WK-K)

      *@       관리한도설정년월일
               MOVE XQJL1241-O-MGT-LIMT-STUP-YMD(WK-L)
                 TO XDJL0419-O-MGT-LIMT-STUP-YMD(WK-K)

      *@       관리한도유효년월일
               MOVE XQJL1241-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD(WK-L)
                 TO XDJL0419-O-VALD-FXDT(WK-K)

220324*    포괄신용관리한도가 0이 아니면(설정상태:설정)이면
               IF XQJL1241-O-INLS-LIMT(WK-L) NOT = ZERO
      *@           여신성자산최고한도＝여신성한도－간접익스포져
                   COMPUTE XDJL0419-O-LNBZ-INCLIN-LIMT(WK-K)
                         = FUNCTION MAX(
                           XQJL1241-O-LNBZ-IA-HGST-LIMT(WK-L) / 1000000,
                           0)

      *@           포괄한도
                   COMPUTE WK-TEMP-INLS-LIMT
                         = XQJL1241-O-INLS-LIMT(WK-L) / 1000000

      *@           2011.06.03추가
      *@          최종포괄한도= MIN(여신성최고한도,포괄한도)
                   COMPUTE XDJL0419-O-INLS-LIMT(WK-K)
                         = FUNCTION MAX(
                           FUNCTION MIN(
                           XDJL0419-O-LNBZ-INCLIN-LIMT(WK-K),
                           WK-TEMP-INLS-LIMT), 0)

220324*@           기사용액 = MIN(사용액, 최종적용 포괄신용공여한도)
                   COMPUTE WK-TEMP-USE-AMT
                         = FUNCTION MAX(
                           FUNCTION MIN(
                           XQJL1241-O-PRVIUS-AMUS(WK-L) / 1000000,
                           XDJL0419-O-INLS-LIMT(WK-K)), 0)

      *@            2011.06.03변경
      *@           소진율=최고포괄한도로　소진율　계산으로　변경
                   INITIALIZE WK-TEMP-EXHS-RT

                   IF XDJL0419-O-INLS-LIMT(WK-K) > 0
                       COMPUTE WK-TEMP-EXHS-RT
                             = WK-TEMP-USE-AMT /
                               XDJL0419-O-INLS-LIMT(WK-K)

                       COMPUTE XDJL0419-O-EXHS-RT(WK-K)
                             = FUNCTION MAX(
                               FUNCTION MIN(
                               WK-TEMP-EXHS-RT * 100, 999.99), 0)
      *@           그렇지않은경우　０으로　산출
                   ELSE
                       MOVE ZERO
                         TO XDJL0419-O-EXHS-RT(WK-K)
                   END-IF
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM

           .
       S3310-QJL1241-OUTPUT-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 협의위원)포괄신용공여한도적정성점검승인조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-QJL2761-CALL-RTN.

      *@   변수초기화
           INITIALIZE                  XQJL2761-IN

      *            그룹회사코드
           MOVE  BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  XQJL2761-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *            고객식별자
           IF    XDJL0419-I-INQURY-CUST-IDNFR    NOT = SPACE

                 MOVE  XDJL0419-I-INQURY-CUST-IDNFR
                   TO  XQJL2761-I-CUST-IDNFR
           ELSE
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-PCT10
                   TO  XQJL2761-I-CUST-IDNFR
           END-IF

      *--        진행상태구분(1전체 2진행중 3완료)
      *          최종한도승인구분 (0:해당무 1:승인 4:불승인)
           EVALUATE  XDJL0419-I-PRGRS-STUS-DSTIC
           WHEN  CO-CHA-1
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-0   TO  XQJL2761-I-LAST-L-ATHOR-DSTCD1
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-4   TO  XQJL2761-I-LAST-L-ATHOR-DSTCD2
           WHEN  CO-CHA-2
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-0   TO  XQJL2761-I-LAST-L-ATHOR-DSTCD1
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-0   TO  XQJL2761-I-LAST-L-ATHOR-DSTCD2
           WHEN  CO-CHA-3
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-1   TO  XQJL2761-I-LAST-L-ATHOR-DSTCD1
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-4   TO  XQJL2761-I-LAST-L-ATHOR-DSTCD2
           END-EVALUATE

      *            신청년월일1
           MOVE  XDJL0419-I-APLCN-YMD1
             TO  XQJL2761-I-APLCN-YMD1
      *            신청년월일2
           MOVE  XDJL0419-I-APLCN-YMD2
             TO  XQJL2761-I-APLCN-YMD2

      *            승인위원직원번호
           IF    XDJL0419-I-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID     = CO-CHA-9999999
                 MOVE  CO-CHA-PCT7
                   TO  XQJL2761-I-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID
           ELSE
                 MOVE  XDJL0419-I-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID
                   TO  XQJL2761-I-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID
           END-IF

      *@   한도신청번호 - NEXT KEY
      *@   자동거래일경우 NEXT KEY 처리한다
           IF BICOM-DSCN-TRAN-DSTCD = CO-CHA-1 OR CO-CHA-2

           #USRLOG  "=================================================="
           #USRLOG  "*                 NEXT    KEY                    *"
           #USRLOG  "=================================================="

              MOVE BOCOM-BF-TDK-INFO-CTNT(1:10)
                TO XQJL2761-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO

              MOVE BOCOM-BF-TDK-INFO-CTNT(11:7)
                TO XQJL2761-I-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID2

           #USRLOG  " LIMT-APLCN-NO : " XQJL2761-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
           #USRLOG  "=================================================="
           END-IF

      *@1.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL2761 XQJL2761-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
